summary: Marketing communications business partner with over 15 years of experience in multi-market settings; from scale-ups to large multinationals. Leading strategy as well as implementation with complex internal and external stakeholder matrix. What drives me: purposeful scope, people, a good challenge to solve, a place where I can keep on learning. Honesty and humanity in what we do. A nature-lover and a foodie.
